==English==
[[Category:English words with multiple etymologies]]

===Pronunciation===
* [[IPA]]: /'pɒd/
*:Rhymes: [[Rhymes:English:-ɒd|-ɒd]]

===Etymology 1===
====Noun====
{{en-noun}}

# {{botany}} a [[seed]] case for legumes (i.e. peas, beans, peppers)
# a small vehicle, especially used in emergency situations.
# (-pod) latin for foot (i.e. tripod (meaning three feet))
=====Derived terms=====
*[[peapod]]
*[[seedpod]]
